{"tid":1896442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"問題嚟啦,點解唔係2016年甚至更早時期大肆進攻功能組別,而係今年先進攻功能組別呢","createTime":"2020-02-25T06:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T07:41:21.000Z","uid":60916,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c623d91084ca709aebe22d32cebfaa2d65a2b8fa","tid":1896442,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:32:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">答案就係泛民係暗共</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解要響美國通過左香港民主人權法，先至黎話要進攻功能組別啊，其實就係要永續功能組別，阻擋香港民主進程。<br />\n果一兩個功能組別議席是小事，佢地後台勢力要阻止香港有民主，有普選。<br />\n<br />\n因為若然香港最終落實雙普選，中共將會喪失對香港既管治權。泛民佢地係知道當美國通過民主人權法案後，要求2020普選立法會，點解佢地唔配合美國爭取普選立法會，以達至雙普選從而成功爭取五大訴求。原因你知我知大家都知<br />\n<br />\n點解佢地會話美國通過一個無咁辣既民主人權法案，原因得1個，因為雙普選後泛民會露底並喪失絕大多數既議席。"},{"pid":"f4bb4a91407e2c8c9ef4384719a2c3aa35a0edb4","tid":1896442,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:32:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9154b8cbf895400ec7635f3f628aa60f42a6b4a","tid":1896442,"uid":122827,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"你啱 所以大家都唔洗抗爭<br />\n中共自然會幫大家落實雙普選"},{"pid":"5b54bf5f4193eaa18e8c7999f31f1dc1359dc7bd","tid":1896442,"uid":60916,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9154b8cbf895400ec7635f3f628aa60f42a6b4a","tid":1896442,"uid":122827,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"你啱 所以大家都唔洗抗爭<br />\n中共自然會幫大家落實雙普選"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"你有冇睇內容架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a6927723de0d28fb1b072bafe84dee38e18a0b","tid":1896442,"uid":228955,"li